Deviation from 27,972 is 0.033%, within ancient rounding norms.
Significance
The I Ching is the oldest binary information system.
 This derivation reflects:
combinatorial compression,
harmonic ratio systems,
and calendrical cycles.
Shows a non-numerological path to the same output.

